'''丽莎·卡林顿女爵士'''，{{post-nominals|post-noms=[[紐西蘭功績勳章|DNZM]]}}（{{lang-en|Dame Lisa Marie Carrington}}，{{bd|1989年|6月23日||}}）<ref name="CR NZ">{{cite web |title=Lisa Carrington |url=http://canoeracing.org.nz/2012-london-olympics/meet-the-olympic-squad/lisa-carrington |publisher=Canoe Racing New Zealand |accessdate=2012-09-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120808070409/http://www.canoeracing.org.nz/2012-london-olympics/meet-the-olympic-squad/lisa-carrington |archivedate=2012-08-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，生于陶朗加，是一名新西兰皮划艇运动员。主攻[[皮艇|皮艇]]竞速。她参加了2012年、2016年和2020年夏季奥运，其中在[[2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会皮划艇比赛|2012年伦敦奥运]]获得一枚金牌，而在[[2016年夏季奥林匹克运动会皮划艇比赛|2016年里约奥运]]获得一金和一铜，並在[[2020年夏季奥林匹克运动会皮划艇比赛|2020年東京奧運]]獲得三枚金牌。

==早年生活==
卡林顿生于陶朗加<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/olympics/other-sports/7462087/Lisa-Carrington-wins-gold-in-K1-200m |title= Carrington wins gold in K1 200m |first= Simon |last= Plumb |publisher= Fairfax Media New Zealand |date= 2012-08-11 |accessdate= 2012-08-14 |archive-date= 2015-09-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150924162748/http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/olympics/other-sports/7462087/Lisa-Carrington-wins-gold-in-K1-200m |dead-url= no }}</ref>，并在[[欧霍普海滩|欧霍普海滩]]（{{lang|en|Ohope Beach}}）长大，她拥有毛利血统<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.radionz.co.nz/news/te-manu-korihi/113146/iwi-hails-carrington%27s-prowess |title= Iwi hails Carrington's prowess |publisher= [[新西蘭國家廣播電台|Radio New Zealand]] |date= 2012-08-13 |accessdate= 2012-08-14 |archive-date= 2013-12-15 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131215161901/http://www.radionz.co.nz/news/te-manu-korihi/113146/iwi-hails-carrington%27s-prowess |dead-url= no }}</ref>。她曾就读于华卡塔尼高中和[[梅西大学|梅西大学]]<ref name="CR NZ"/>。她的教练是Gordon Walker<ref name="CR NZ"/>。

==运动生涯==
2009年6月，卡林顿参加了皮划艇世界杯匈牙利站的比赛，并在女子双人皮艇1000米上获得一枚铜牌<ref>{{cite news|last=Leggat|first=David|title=Kayaking: Custom boat helps get speed up|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/new-zealand/news/article.cfm?l_id=71&objectid=10590391|accessdate=2012-07-19|newspaper=New Zealand herald|date=2009-08-13|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304071417/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/new-zealand/news/article.cfm?l_id=71&objectid=10590391|dead-url=no}}</ref>2010年5月，她在皮划艇世界杯法国站的比赛中获得同一小项的金牌<ref>{{cite news|last=Cleaver|first=Dylan|title=Kayaking: Young Kiwis paddle to first in K2 1000|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/sport/news/article.cfm?c_id=4&objectid=10643908|accessdate=2012-07-19|newspaper=New Zealand Herald|date=2010-05-10|archive-date=2014-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140112013926/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/sport/news/article.cfm?c_id=4&objectid=10643908|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

之后卡林顿在2010年大洋洲皮划艇锦标赛上赢得双人皮艇500米和1000米以及四人皮艇500米的冠军<ref>{{cite news|title=Kiwis take three Oceania kayaking golds|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/3327565/Kiwis-take-three-Oceania-kayaking-golds|accessdate=2012-07-19|date=2010-02-14|agency=New Zealand Press Association|archive-date=2019-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190922040043/http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/3327565/Kiwis-take-three-Oceania-kayaking-golds|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而后，卡林顿和搭档Teneale Hatton在[[2010年世界輕艇競速錦標賽|2010年世界輕艇競速錦標賽]]上闯进A组决赛，成为第一对达成此成就的新西兰运动员，在决赛中她们最终获得第9名<ref name=final>{{cite news|title=Kiwi women qualify for kayaking final|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/4047596/Kiwi-women-qualify-for-kayaking-final|accessdate=2012-07-19|date=2010-08-21|agency=New Zealand Press Association|archive-date=2019-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190917183147/http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/4047596/Kiwi-women-qualify-for-kayaking-final|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在[[匈牙利|匈牙利]][[塞格德|塞格德]]举办的2011年世锦赛上，卡林顿赢得了女子单人皮艇200米的冠军，成为史上第一位在皮划艇竞速世锦赛上赢得冠军的新西兰女子运动员<ref>{{cite news|title=Carrington restores canoeing credibility|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/olympic-games/news/article.cfm?c_id=502&objectid=10803313|accessdate=2012-07-19|newspaper=New Zealand Herald|date=2012-05-04|agency=New Zealand Press Association|archive-date=2012-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120530083235/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/olympic-games/news/article.cfm?c_id=502&objectid=10803313|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而她也为新西兰争取到了该项目的奥运席位<ref name=ICF>{{cite web|title=Australia Secures three Olympic Quotas at Oceania Championships|url=http://www.canoeicf.com/icf/NewsGallery/News-Archive/March-2012/Australia-Earns-three-additional-spots-at-London-2012.html|publisher=[[國際輕艇總會|International Canoe federation]]|accessdate=2012-07-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120801164108/http://www.canoeicf.com/icf/NewsGallery/News-Archive/March-2012/Australia-Earns-three-additional-spots-at-London-2012.html|archivedate=2012-08-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年年底，她因为在世锦赛上的出色表现获得了新西兰年度最佳成年[[毛利人|毛利族]]女运动员的荣誉<ref>{{cite web |title=Lisa Carrington wins Maori Sports Award |url=http://canoeracing.org.nz/Home-1/News/Archive/2011/Maori-Sports-Awards-honours?c9003cp=31&c9003ps=3 |publisher=Canoe Racing New Zealand |accessdate=2012-08-12 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121220222432/http://canoeracing.org.nz/Home-1/News/Archive/2011/Maori-Sports-Awards-honours?c9003cp=31&c9003ps=3 |archivedate=2012-12-20 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2012年8月，卡林顿代表新西兰参加了在[[英国|英国]][[伦敦|伦敦]]举办的第30届夏季奥运<ref>{{cite news|last=Plumb|first=Simon|title=Kayaker Lisa Carrington has eyes on gold|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/olympics/6856817/Kayaker-Lisa-Carrington-has-eyes-on-gold|accessdate=2012-07-19|date=2012-05-04|agency=Fairfax NZ News|archive-date=2012-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120506123704/http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/olympics/6856817/Kayaker-Lisa-Carrington-has-eyes-on-gold|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她首先和搭档Erin Taylor在[[2012年夏季奧林匹克運動會輕艇女子500公尺雙人愛斯基摩艇|女子双人皮艇500米]]项目上获得第7名，之后她在女子单人皮艇200米上赢得个人首枚奥运金牌<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.olympic.org.nz/assets/Uploads/NZOC-Olympic-Stories-Lisa-Carrington-FINAL.pdf|title=Lisa Carrington - New Zealand Olympic Team|publisher=[[紐西蘭奧林匹克委員會|New Zealand Olympic Committee]]|accessdate=2016-10-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022042153/http://www.olympic.org.nz/assets/Uploads/NZOC-Olympic-Stories-Lisa-Carrington-FINAL.pdf|archivedate=2016-10-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

伦敦奥运后，卡林顿在2013、2014和2015年世锦赛的女子单人皮艇200米项目上都获得冠军，达成了世锦赛该项目的四连冠。除此之外，她还分别在2013年、2014年和2015年世锦赛的单人皮艇500米项目上获得铜牌、银牌和金牌。

2016年8月，卡林顿赴[[巴西|巴西]][[里约热内卢|里约热内卢]]参加第31届夏季奥运，首先她在女子单人皮艇200米项目上成功卫冕<ref name="NZH2016-K1200m-gold">{{cite news | url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/sport/news/article.cfm?c_id=4&objectid=11695201 | title=NZ Herald Olympics Banner Rio Olympics 2016: Lisa Carrington claims gold in K1 200m | work=[[新西兰先驱报|The New Zealand Herald]] | date=2016-08-17 | accessdate=2016-08-17 | archive-date=2016-08-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817221759/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/sport/news/article.cfm?c_id=4&objectid=11695201 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，之后她又获得了女子单人皮艇500米的铜牌<ref>{{cite news |last1=Hinton |first1=Marc |title=Rio Olympics 2016: Lisa Carrington claims bronze in women's K1 500m final |url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/olympics/83336154/rio-olympics-2016-lisa-carrington-claims-bronze-in-womens-k1-500m-final |accessdate=2016-08-22 |work=Stuff.co.nz |date=2016-08-19 |archive-date=2017-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170708082937/http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/olympics/83336154/rio-olympics-2016-lisa-carrington-claims-bronze-in-womens-k1-500m-final |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她在里约奥运上的出色表现也让她获选为该届奥运[[2016年夏季奥林匹克运动会新西兰代表团|新西兰代表团]]的闭幕式旗手<ref>{{cite news |title=Rio Olympics 2016: Lisa Carrington to carry the NZ flag at closing ceremony |url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/olympics/news/article.cfm?c_id=502&objectid=11698545 |accessdate=2016-08-22 |work=The New Zealand Herald |date=2016-08-22 |archive-date=2018-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629211329/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/olympics/news/article.cfm?c_id=502&objectid=11698545 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2017年至2019年世锦赛期间，卡林顿共收获5枚金牌、4枚银牌和1枚铜牌。5枚金牌中有3枚来自于女子单人皮艇200米，她也凭借这一表现达成该项目的七连冠。4枚银牌中全部来自于500米项目，其中有3枚来自于2018年世锦赛。

2021年8月，卡林頓在[[日本|日本]][[東京|東京]]的第32屆夏季奧運上達成女子單人皮艇200米項目三連霸，並於女子單人皮艇500米及女子雙人皮艇500米項目斬獲金牌。

==奖项与荣誉==
卡林顿于2012年11月获得新西兰年度最佳毛利族运动员奖以及年度最佳成年毛利族女运动员奖<ref name="">{{cite web |url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/other-sports/7994753/Carrington-wins-Maori-Sportsperson-of-the-Year |title=Carrington wins Maori Sportsperson of Year |publisher=Fairfax Media |date=2012-11-24 |accessdate=2012-11-25 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924163400/http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/other-sports/7994753/Carrington-wins-Maori-Sportsperson-of-the-Year |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之后她也因为在皮艇运动上作出不小的贡献而获得新西兰攻绩勋章<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.dpmc.govt.nz/node/1121 |title= New Year Honours List 2013 |publisher= Department of the Prime Minister and Cabinet |date= 2012-12-31 |accessdate= 2012-12-31 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130101160253/http://www.dpmc.govt.nz/node/1121 |archivedate= 2013-01-01 }}</ref>。2017年，她又获得2016年度哈尔伯格奖年度最佳女运动员奖以及最高奖<ref name="2016 Halberg Awards">{{cite news |last1=Burgess |first1=Michael |title=Lisa Carrington queen of sport with Halberg Awards wins |url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/sport/news/article.cfm?c_id=4&objectid=11797863 |accessdate=2017-02-09 |work=The New Zealand Herald |date=2017-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170210003633/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/sport/news/article.cfm?c_id=4&objectid=11797863 |archive-date=2017-02-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

卡林頓在紐西蘭{{link-en|2022新年榮譽（紐西蘭）|2022 New Year Honours (New Zealand)|2022新年榮譽}}中頒授[[紐西蘭功績勳章|紐西蘭爵級同伴功績勳章]]（DNZM），以表彰她「對皮艇的貢獻」。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/new-year-honours-the-full-list-of-2022/EOKFR77H542D647EWBSCHNSBKI/ |title=New Year Honours: the full list of 2022 |date=2021-12-31 |work=New Zealand Herald |accessdate=2022-01-02 |archive-date=2021-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211230225555/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/new-year-honours-the-full-list-of-2022/EOKFR77H542D647EWBSCHNSBKI/ }}</ref>

